    <title class="- topic/title " xtrc="title:1;4:12" xtrf="file:/C:/Users/jheckel/Documents/Repositories/Spectre/Spectre/docs/Database-Documentation/topics/database-administrator-guide-topic.dita">ECOMAPP Database Architecture</title>
    <shortdesc class="- topic/shortdesc " xtrc="shortdesc:1;5:16" xtrf="file:/C:/Users/jheckel/Documents/Repositories/Spectre/Spectre/docs/Database-Documentation/topics/database-administrator-guide-topic.dita">The database design and architecture includes SKU composition, multiplier-based
        pricing, and normalized entities with referential integrity. NXTCG ECOMAPP's database is
        hosted on Db2 13 for z/OS.</shortdesc>
